                <condition>
                  <list>
                    <item>
                      <p>Vellum, about 11 1/4 in. by 7 1/4, consisting of 59 leaves, the first and
                        last of which are blank. <locus>Foll. 1—3</locus> have been almost completely torn out, and
                        <locus>fol. 58</locus> is slightly injured. The quires, signed with letters, are 6 in
                        number. A single leaf is wanting after <locus>fol. 58</locus>. Each page is divided into
                        two columns, of from 20 to 24 lines.</p>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </condition>
              </supportDesc>
